pullrequest.title: qtutils 2.0.0 support and experimental PyQt5 support

content.raw:
I had 3 Ni Cards and a pulseblaster attached they were in no error state not sure if they were calling the worker process. I might do a more active test on monday wehere I let them run a few shots.
